{"tid":1111677,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"隔牆有耳：傑出校友689「數」理大 粉絲盲跟 插爆「廢大暴徒」 - 李八方","createTime":"2019-04-17T04:15:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T04:58:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2153bbd27b92943c9eb56b54970b6cb4372f5057","tid":1111677,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T04:15:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190417/20657759\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190417%2F20657759&d=cvAaz42KU7EB3jG3uroQKGyAt0yGCUsyxQooKadsmXE%3D&h=c6651226\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190417%2F20657759&h=e90e1e54\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190417/20657759</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：傑出校友689「數」理大<br />\n粉絲盲跟 插爆「廢大暴徒」 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190417/large/a0904a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190417%2Flarge%2Fa0904a.gif&h=e4acb99b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n前行政長官、政協副主席梁振英狙擊《蘋果》廣告，點知今次狙擊竟然狙擊返佢自己！仲俾網民恥笑佢俾自己粉絲鬧返佢「廢」、係「暴徒」，點解689今次咁失策？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190417/large/a0904b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190417%2Flarge%2Fa0904b.gif&h=6a23be78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n全宇宙最得閒嘅689昨日繼續數《蘋果》全版廣告，客戶係理大專上學院。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190417/large/a0904c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190417%2Flarge%2Fa0904c.gif&h=a689bee6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n74年測量學高級文憑畢業<br />\n<br />\n話說689噚日又喺fb發文，指「今（昨）日《蘋果》只有一版全版廣告」，客戶係理工大學專上學院，咁佢班粉絲梗係跟住鬧理大，有人留言「理大專收黃屍？」、「垃圾學生才會去讀」、「廢大即是廢大，專產暴徒」等等，不過佢班粉絲冇為意，689其實都係理大出身，佢1974年喺理大前身、理工學院測量學高級文憑畢業，1997年仲獲校方表揚為「傑出理大校友」，有網民即時轉貼加附和689班粉絲，話佢哋真係鬧得啱，話理大真係出過好出名嘅「暴徒」，又有人話垃圾學生先讀理大，唔知又包唔包作為「傑出理大校友」嘅689呢？<br />\n<br />\n其實有689粉絲都知瀨嘢，喺留言度補飛，話689係以前理大學生，又話689讀理大年代，學生有水平高素質，所以689做特首受香港特區市民擁護喎，雖然叫做可以幫689兜到，但就兜得好夾硬，而且689班粉絲留言鬧理大前，為乜冇諗到會燒埋689呢？似乎都要檢討吓喎。<br />\n<br />\n李八方  <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n江湖滾熱辣 (尊子)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n隔牆有耳：拍住高官政要主禮 栗潛心現身？ (李八方)"},{"pid":"cbb463de62c8942b7c2a2af13099b510c6cc5f11","tid":1111677,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T04:17:10.000Z","msg":"個班人應該係文革餘孽"},{"pid":"bc5322a9f1fb8186dec03986e0e576c3e0cbf9ac","tid":1111677,"uid":55597,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T04:50:28.000Z","msg":"理大專出垃圾，所以出左689"},{"pid":"ff95b5eede532dac8ddc0aab154974b5e360da1d","tid":1111677,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T04:58:56.000Z","msg":"共產黨面前，怎會有「母校」這些倫理的觀念呢？一國行先，斬死老母都無問題喇"}]}